					<div class="col-md-7">

						<h4 class="heading-primary mb-sm">Project <strong>Description</strong></h4>
						<p>Virtual reality application devoted to data exploration, with particular focus on dimensionality reduction and clustering techniques. This research project represents a first attempt to leverage MR/VR technology to better analyze complex multidimensional datasets, which require interactive experimentation, automation and better perspective on the data in order to achieve meaningful insights.</p><a href="https://youtu.be/_y82sUmOWHQ" target="_blank" class="btn btn-success">Video</a> <span class="arrow hlb"></span>
